IT’S COFFEE TIME 🎶 ☕️❤️ I am beyond excited to share @ilovebruvi with you all! I am a BIG coffee drinker ( parents you feel me on this one 😜 ) and this new brewer is BEYOND phenomenal. I had my first cup at a girlfriends house and immediately wanted one. Some of the many awesome features are the touchscreen, you can customize your cup of joe to be hotter, lower acidity or stronger & it has an actual cold brew option as well. It’s chic and looks beautiful on any counter top. The BPods hold more coffee than regular pods and the recycling of these pods are designed to be wayyyyy better for the environment. They breakdown in landfills more rapidly, so you can feel guilt free about tossing when done 🫶🏻
And lastly the coffee is GOOD, like really good. Run don’t walk and upgrade to a Bruvi, I promise you will love ❤️☕️ #bruvi #coffeelover

A little piece from a favorite poem of mine which was written by a woman on her
85th birthday ...
"Oh, I’ve had my moments and if I had it to do over
again, I'd have more of them. In fact, I'd try to have nothing else. Just moments.
One after another, instead of living so many years ahead of each day. "
I love this. 
As I celebrate turning another year older I filled the day with moments that I will cherish forever. A great dinner with the best girlfriends, a peaceful morning hike & meditation and sweets with my lil angel who by the way is starting to TALK. I knowwwwww, my heart 🥹💓
Cheers friends & thank you for all the birthday love 🥂🎉
Now, let's go have some more moments shall we  Xoxo

🎉5!!!!🎉 Holy WOW! I can’t believe 5 years ago at 3:05 am Halloween morning I birthed a beautiful baby girl in a tub full of warm water, surrounded by twinkle lights while Michael repeatedly said Lavender to me before I quietly told him to shhhhhhhh in between contractions ( in his defense that was what he was taught to say from our hypnobirthing classes lol ) 
It’s said by many mamas when you give birth your heart is now living outside of your body and that is absolutely what it feels like. She’s the best thing to ever happen to me and continues to be my greatest teacher in life. 🥹❤️🎂
#birthdaybath #halloweenbaby
